<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Car Detailing - CarWashPro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4f7, #cce0f4);
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .image {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .content {
            flex: 2;
        }
        .content h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .features {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .features li {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .features li::before {
            content: "✔";
            color: #007BFF;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .back-button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="image">
            <img src="/images/car_details.jpg" alt="Car Detailing">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Professional Car Detailing</h2>
            <p>Experience top-notch car detailing services to give your vehicle a brand-new look. Our experts ensure high-quality cleaning and detailing for both interior and exterior.</p>
            <ul class="features">
                <li>Full Interior & Exterior Detailing</li>
                <li>High-Quality Waxing & Polishing</li>
                <li>Deep Carpet & Upholstery Cleaning</li>
                <li>Headlight Restoration</li>
                <li>Engine Bay Cleaning</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/services" class="back-button">← Back to Services</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
